# ORBISAVE FRONTEND SYSTEM DESIGN CHECKLIST
> Purpose: Guide AI agents to build a high-quality, scalable, secure, and visually engaging frontend system.
> This is NOT a generic UI. It must reflect Orbisave’s identity as a collective capital coordination platform.

---

## 1. CORE FRONTEND PRINCIPLES

- [ ] UI must feel **premium, alive, and intentional** (NOT template-like)
- [ ] Animations must **communicate meaning**, not decoration
- [ ] UX must support:
  - [ ] Low-tech users (farmers)
  - [ ] High-level users (corporates)
- [ ] Mobile-first design
- [ ] Accessibility considered (contrast, readability)

---

## 2. TECH STACK

- [ ] Framework: Next.js (App Router)
- [ ] Styling: Tailwind CSS
- [ ] Animations: GSAP (primary)
- [ ] State/Data:
  - [ ] TanStack Query (server state)
  - [ ] Zustand (local state if needed)
- [ ] Auth:
  - [ ] Better Auth integrated with DRF backend
- [ ] Forms:
  - [ ] React Hook Form + Zod validation

---

