## 14. UX EDGE CASES

- [ ] User joins multiple groups
- [ ] User has no activity
- [ ] Slow network users
- [ ] Partial onboarding

---

## 15. FINAL CHECK

- [ ] Landing page feels unique (NOT template)
- [ ] Animations explain the system clearly
- [ ] Onboarding prevents empty groups
- [ ] Roles enforced correctly
- [ ] Security is solid
- [ ] Works smoothly on mobile

